14:36.208 --> 14:37.197
Hi.

14:39.778 --> 14:41.302
I was just...

14:45.551 --> 14:46.882
Come on up.

14:49.054 --> 14:50.248
MARSHALL: He's in.

14:51.557 --> 14:55.789
So, Ranjit, you must have done it
with a Lebanese girl?

14:55.895 --> 14:58.159
Okay, that's my Barney limit.

14:58.264 --> 15:00.459
I'm gonna see
if that bodega has a bathroom.

15:01.367 --> 15:04.302
Actually, I'm from Bangladesh.

15:04.403 --> 15:07.930
- The women hot there?
- Here's a picture of my wife.

15:10.109 --> 15:12.043
(WHISPERING) A simple "no"
would have sufficed.

15:13.812 --> 15:15.245
She's lovely.

15:16.482 --> 15:21.146
So, Ted, what brings you back to Brooklyn
at 1:00 in the morning in a suit?

15:22.755 --> 15:24.518
I was just hoping to

15:25.357 --> 15:26.756
get those olives

15:27.126 --> 15:29.185
that you said I could have.

15:29.295 --> 15:32.355
Would you like those olives
with some gin and vermouth?

15:32.464 --> 15:34.728
Are you trying to get me drunk?

15:38.837 --> 15:40.634
For starters.

15:41.106 --> 15:42.630
<i>(MUSIC PLA YING)</i>

15:44.276 --> 15:45.903
Thank you.

15:47.680 --> 15:51.116
So, Marshall,
this Olive Theory based on you and Lily.

15:51.216 --> 15:52.911
- Yeah.
- You hate olives.

15:53.018 --> 15:56.215
- Lily loves them, you can't stand them.
- Yeah, I hate olives.

15:56.322 --> 15:58.517
Two weeks ago,
Spanish bar on 79th Street.

15:58.624 --> 16:01.024
Dish of olives. You had some. What up?

16:04.697 --> 16:07.530
You have to swear
that this does not leave this cab.

16:07.733 --> 16:09.758
- I swear.
- I swear.

16:12.037 --> 16:14.505
On our first date, I ordered a Greek salad.

16:14.606 --> 16:16.699
Lily asked if she could have my olives.

16:16.809 --> 16:19.209
I said, "Sure, I hate olives."

16:19.311 --> 16:20.972
But you like olives.

16:21.080 --> 16:23.640
Well, I was 18, okay? I was a virgin.

16:23.749 --> 16:26.718
Been waiting my whole life
for a pretty girl to want my olives.

16:27.987 --> 16:31.013
Marshall, I'm gonna give you
an early wedding present.

16:31.123 --> 16:32.750
Don't get married.

